<bibRefCitation author="Fowler" box="[779,921,1469,1492]" pageId="2" refString="Fowler, W. W. (1895) Order Rhynchota. Suborder Hemiptera-Homoptera. (Continued). In: Porter, R. H. (Ed.), Biologia Centrali- Americana; or, Contributions to the knowledge of the fauna and flora of Mexico and Central America, 2. Porter, London, pp. 57 - 72." type="journal article" year="1895">Fowler, 1895</bibRefCitation>
